				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Some people seem to think shamans kite.  This isnt the ideal way for a shaman to solo.  When you kite your damage on the DoTs go down by 33%, and face it we cant nuke for crap.  Its best to keep a target rooted and DoT it.  Re-root as nessecary.  This might not work with regular 'ol root as well, but when you get enstill kiting is crazy unless you are real real good with your pet.  Personally I soloed a giant that I estimated had 6k hitpoints with enstill and Venom of Snake.  Just say no to kiting.
				</font>
